title: WHIRLING F1 / Alain 2 barks post tribunal
description: barks for Alain if Titus got shit in tribunal

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""... no worse than the bangers on B..."
dialogueTree.english: "... no worse than the bangers on Boogie Street."
dialogueTree.polish: „...nie gorsi od gangusów z Boogie Street”.

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""*This* is gonna make a hell of a s..."
dialogueTree.english: "*This* is gonna make a hell of a sad tattoo..."

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Theo went like he lived -- fast an..."
dialogueTree.english: "Theo went like he lived -- fast and hard. Tough old man."
dialogueTree.polish: „Theo zginął tak, jak żył. Szybko i z jebnięciem. Stary twardziel”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Тэо загінуў так, як жыў. Хутка і з выбухам. Стары цвыркун".

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""We could take over the entire city.""
dialogueTree.english: "We could take over the entire city."

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Alain is a fucking roach name anyw..."
dialogueTree.english: "Alain is a fucking roach name anyway... So *me*."
dialogueTree.polish: „Alain to imię jak dla robaka... Idealne *dla mnie*”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Ален – гэта імя, як для чарвяка... Ідэальна *для мяне*".

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""I'm the lucky fuck, who didn't tak..."
dialogueTree.english: "I'm the lucky fuck, who didn't take a scratch." (Sighs.)
dialogueTree.polish: „Jestem fartowny skurwiel, którego nawet nie tknęli” – mówi, wzdychając.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я шчаслівы лайдакуха, да якога нават не дакрануліся", — кажа ён, уздыхаючы.

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Ain't no one gonna be writing any..."
dialogueTree.english: "Ain't no one gonna be writing any ballads about me..."
dialogueTree.polish: „O mnie nikt ballad pisał nie będzie...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Пра мяне ніхто балад пісаць не будзе..."

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Shanky's gonna get a lesson in Boo..."
dialogueTree.english: "Shanky's gonna get a lesson in Boogie Street justice."
dialogueTree.polish: „Kosior dostanie lekcję sprawiedliwości rodem z Boogie Street”.

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Gonna hunt that rat-faced fuck dow..."
Alain: ""For Titus... for Glenny... for......"
dialogueTree.english: "For Titus... for Glenny... for... for Titus!!!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Za Titusa... za Glenny'ego... Za... za Titusa!!!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "За Тытуса... за Гленні... За... за Тытуса!!!"

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""When it's done I'll just blow my b..."
dialogueTree.english: "When it's done I'll just blow my brains out... Fuck everything."
dialogueTree.polish: „Jak to się skończy, to se po prostu odstrzelę łeb... Jebać to wszystko”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Як гэта скончыцца, то проста адстралю сабе галаву... Напляваць на ўсё гэта".

dialogueTree.title: Alain: ""Boogie street justice. Gonna make..."
dialogueTree.english: "Boogie street justice. Gonna make you proud, T."
dialogueTree.polish: „Sprawiedliwość rodem z Boogie Street. Będziesz ze mnie dumny, T”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Справядлівасць з Багі-стрыт. Будзеш мною ганарыцца, T".
